Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是像你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就到了  再乖乖地坐一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  满潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到了濑户内海的奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  巴士一小时只有一班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓一跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从傍晚开始  连一班车都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说这才是稀松平常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛  在埼玉这样的城市长大的小孩是不会懂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  你情绪好高涨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好久没回来过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们直到刚才还是在海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  大海和山很近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往右看是海  往左看是山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是濑户内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路还这么窄  都快要翻车滚下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄上次来的时候年纪还很小啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已经记不太清了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶  是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  爷爷也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  难得回来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让你准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊  要是每年都能回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很难拿到假期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就撇下丈夫  你跟永澄两个回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了  这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄也是呢  昨天才终于补习完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我想起些痛苦的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是暑假  每天还得往学校跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是补习完了  就不带你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分  这什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你成绩差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你老爸学习更差  不过现在也混得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娶了个好媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有了个可爱的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事情都让你碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你是「可爱的儿子」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:06:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个差劲的家伙  不过以后也要拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起呢  连孙子也这么差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下是各地的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四国地区  由于受东内海为中心的高气压影响  将放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一下子就脱衣服啊  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一回来就这么激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  一个小孩子却半点朝气都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该更像昭和年间的小孩那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对暑假这一珍贵的瞬间  流着鼻涕狂喜乱舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子里的小孩子是何种概念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊  我是平成出生的  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  你不会游泳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话啊  我怎么可能不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要沉了  好难受…呼吸不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受  要死了  完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来  谁来  谁来救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  喂  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  正奇怪怎么到处都不见人影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么跑到这里睡大觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你被水淹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是你老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要回奶奶家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我的确是溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海里溺水了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溺水了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说是溺水之后被冲到岩壁这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的确…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…你被人鱼救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？人鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还当真啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡糊涂了  要回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老爸  等一下我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我的确是溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦  老爸  听我说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄被人鱼救了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的  奶奶  我都看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说些羞人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这点是像谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是像你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埼玉没有人鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  别听他瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我真的看到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在濑户内  特别是这附近  自古就有人鱼传说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人鱼传说？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果传说是真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  永澄不过是暑假痴呆症罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才痴呆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这点是像谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你们啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  长头发  很像人鱼的那干爽蓬松的秀发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这么晚还有客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱的女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就跟这女孩一样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁家的姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫濑户灿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户灿…你是永澄的熟人么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他在这里没有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我…和永澄结婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  事出突然  各位一定受惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我希望永澄对白天的事情负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对白天的事情负责…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泼皮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙在我不知道的时候干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然逼我不惜使出左钩拳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溺水了啊  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前  泼皮是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是个初中生就搞出人命  你这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这孩子真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  妈妈  不知道你在说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜打搅  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑帮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过中间那个人挺有型的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥人妻杀手的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成怎样我可不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  你们都给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是灿小姐的自家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想劳亲家们大驾  移步到寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和灿小姐的父母  我们的老大直接会面谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是黑帮的千金！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  这回事情不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  能问一下为什么要带我们到这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  请各位先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙是想杀了我们吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不肖子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖着我下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持不了呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人人…人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是白天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤婿  贤婿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧  贤婿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿政
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我起来  我起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～明知道这是不应该的却…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒过来吧  孩子他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也关心一下我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这里是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的初吻对象是政先生么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头我们好好谈谈吧  孩子她妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你现在很是混乱嘛  贤婿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  这里到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是小灿的家啊  在海底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人鱼之家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远道而来  辛苦了  客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子是灿的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户内鱼类联合濑户内组组长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户豪三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他妻子  濑户莲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是地道正宗的黑帮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点是像谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让诸位远道而来不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我女儿救了令郎一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟妈妈说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我被人鱼救了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说吧  客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人鱼有这么一个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟人类扯上关系并被看到真身的人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要判死刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要变成海泡消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也拿这规定没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  是不是很可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的错啊  靠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺家小灿为啥救了人还得去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想让我怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以老子想了个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果暴露了真身要判死刑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把知道真身的人分尸就没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要推我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  冷静点  老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的  包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是母子幻想暴走的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开  放开老子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话  那我救他就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随意救人然后又随意杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这违反了「仁义之道」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小灿  我们人鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是我救的  不会半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯彻到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  要杀要剐悉听尊便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿  不要说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  让爸爸干掉这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情势自然而然地在恶化了  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸你是家长  快帮忙稳定局面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  我老公血气上头  就完全不能指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家女儿也是  平时虽然很温顺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也很倔强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想到一个能让永澄和小灿都免去一死的好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说！莲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我家小灿结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道小灿真身的是自己人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有任何问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  你能当人鱼的女婿么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄的父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然心里很难过  但就是这么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我可爱动人的小灿结婚就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  只有把知道我们身份的人类全部杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也明白吧  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是知道我们身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们都消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂这话吧  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好的吗  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  有个这么好的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种看着我的脸说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话啊  爸爸一直都会守护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那传说中的左钩拳怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸那招一天只能用一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能娶我女儿  还有什么不满的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没没有不满啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这这这这是感情问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠旁人决定的话…是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间也不熟悉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  该死的孑孓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿都已经下定决心了  你还唧唧歪歪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种废渣  我怎么会把我家小灿交给你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剁了你就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  你要让女儿一生的觉悟白费掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿政  别让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…我初吻的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都已经死过一次了  还是乖乖地去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑啊你  不会让你跑掉的  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大门怎么打不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼去哪里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着水流进到里面去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬碎他  鲨藤代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨藤代？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是鲨鱼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  藤代先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的食饵去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  你叫作…小灿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  我们从后门逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一味地被救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直往前走的话就能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.88,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fish Tail(鱼尾)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陆地的话就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要逃跑的只是永澄吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样跑掉的话  小灿就会死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧吧  小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸还会追过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你爸爸啊  不是岳父啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是带着我走的话  爸爸肯定会追你到天涯海角哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  为什么你不惜破戒来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  眼前的人有困难都不去帮的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有损我们濑户内人鱼的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写作「仁侠」  读作「人鱼」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能因我任性做的事给永澄带来困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄自己逃就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  该死的孑孓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找得我好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为逃得出我的手掌心吗  你这臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我上  蛸中岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼到～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过声音好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All in one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤婿  相处的时光真是短暂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算逃跑  就算逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:31.73,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:32.53,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.03,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是不会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  要死的不是小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你  臭小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把女儿交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就按照对小灿有利的方式来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在形式上结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再让小灿做自己想做的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那样盯着我  会害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的孑孓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿是我可爱动人的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子都不会嫁人啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  这才是你的真正想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候让女儿离开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  打我女儿主意的害虫都要抱着石头沉入濑户内海喂鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命就这么不值钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天  濑户内海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  满潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到奶奶家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  娶了个人鱼老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  岳父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你岳父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我沉下去吧  杀千刀的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的她是濑户内的人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是黑帮的千金  女仁侠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  到夏祭了  和她去约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会不会积极过头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  凡事开头是最关键的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好展示自己帅气的方面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有那种方面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.50,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&Hffffff&\shad0}次回  戒指故事


